IPay88 PHP class
================
This is a simple wrapper class to integrate IPay88 payment gateway (http://www.ipay88.com) in Malaysia.

Usage
-----
Refer to request.php and response.php for sample code on how to use.

For recurring payments, please refer to request.php as well on how to use. The code has been merged into this class.
The callback sample is at recurring_response.php
